snippet.title: Ohka BOTS | Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Ohka BOTS is a free-to-play action role-playing multiplayer online game available for PC.

Join the Ohka BOTS open beta!
http://ohkabots.ohkaspace.com/#/Homehttp://ohkaspace.com/

Ohka BOTS: A battle to save Cyberspace and become the strongest BOT you can be. Upgrade and customize your BOT as you power up and loot your way through the Virus threat that has infested Cyberspace.


Take on other BOTS in fast paced PvP or hire mercenaries and join Base vs Base battles.
